00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:22,070
沃尔玛达78亿美元
to the tune of 7.8 billion dollars a year,

188
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,610
给超过一成的员工
by issuing food stamps to

189
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:27,190
