Well, I'm not appealing to the cynical side.

254
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:13,990
你继续健身吧
I'll leave you to your workout.

255
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:16,420
你现在可是有孩子的人
You have kids now.

256
00:14:18,590 --> 00:14:19,980
我有丈夫  他有孩子
I have a husband. He has kids.

257
