275
00:15:15,590 --> 00:15:16,460
"密切合作"
"Working closely"?

276
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:19,950
我也天天谴责你但还是跟你密切合作
Well, I condemn you every day but I still work closely with you.

277
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,790
这个电话我得接
So, I need to take this phone call.

278
00:15:24,830 --> 00:15:26,350
润色一下  再拿给我
Punch it up, bring it back to me.

279
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:30,080
-道格  -我有个口信给总统
- Doug? - I have a message for the president.

280
00:15:30,690 --> 00:15:31,470
是什么
What is it?

281
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:34,080
告诉他杰姬和邓巴今晚在迪比克市碰过面
Tell him Jackie and Dunbar met in Dubuque tonight.

282
00:15:34,730 --> 00:15:36,220
告诉他是我告诉你的
And tell him I'm the one who told you.

283
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:38,160
她们为何碰面
What did they meet about?

284
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:40,890
在飓风到后她们要暂停竞选活动
Suspending their campaigns after the hurricane hits.

285
00:15:41,900 --> 00:15:44,310
-你怎么知道的  -告诉他就行
- How do you know this? - Just tell him.

286
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:47,130
你在秘密为杰姬工作吗
Are you working for Jackie, under the radar?

287
00:15:47,190 --> 00:15:49,080
-不是  -为邓巴
- No. - Dunbar?

288
00:15:49,430 --> 00:15:51,190
我仅仅是为总统着想
I'm just looking out for the president.

289
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:54,930
告诉他这个消息还有消息的来源
Give him the information and tell him who it came from.

290
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:56,980
有进一步消息我通知你
I'll let you know if I learn more.

291
00:15:56,800 --> 00:16:00,430
{\pos(166.8,138.15)}{\an7}飓风费斯正在接近

292
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:07,410
"海水冰冷  水流湍急
"The water was cold and the current was strong.

293
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:10,720
男孩每次划水都必须击退寒冷
With every stroke, the boy had to fight off chills

294
00:16:10,770 --> 00:16:13,490
抵抗大海涌来的激流
and battle the tide rushing in from the sea.

295
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:16,740
从海岸上望着他的同学们
Anyone watching him, as his schoolmates did from the shore,

296
00:16:16,910 --> 00:16:20,390
几乎辨认不出水面上缓慢移动的小点
barely making out a tiny speck moving slowly across the water,

297
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:22,560
都觉得他没希望了
would've thought he stood no chance.

298
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:25,840
但男孩从未这么想过
But that thought never entered the boy's mind.

299
00:16:26,610 --> 00:16:29,660
他肌肉酸痛  心跳剧烈
His muscles ached, his heart pounded,

300
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:32,930
但海水无法将他打败"
but the water would not defeat him."

301
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,570
我想利用体育馆和市政厅
I want rec centers and town halls,

302
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:37,820
但最重要的是学校
but the most important thing is schools.

303
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:38,810
它们是关键所在
They're the key.

304
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:42,100
俄亥俄以东的每所学校
Well, every school east of Ohio.

305
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,510
告诉那些不同意的州长
You tell the governors that push back,

306
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:46,730
我们会用赈灾资金余款
tell them we'll pay for the shutdown days

307
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:48,760
补偿停摆和加班损失
and overtime with what's left in the DRF.

308
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,290
不  我们会想出
No, we'll figure out how to

309
00:16:50,290 --> 00:16:52,660
用其他部门把人转移过去的办法
get people there through some other department.

310
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:54,730
先搞定学校
Just get me the schools!

311
00:16:56,190 --> 00:16:58,080
我一直告诉他们别给我送那个了
I keep telling them to stop bringing those.

312
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,690
我知道  是我给你的
I know. I got these myself.

313
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:02,050
谢谢  你真贴心
Oh, thank you. That's sweet.

314
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:04,650
-有进展了吗  -有点  但还不够
- Any progress? - Some, but not enough.

315
00:17:06,700 --> 00:17:09,650
你今天举手是真心的吗
Did you mean it today, when you raised your hand?

316
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:10,920
不是
No.

317
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,370
但我知道如果我举手
But I knew if I did,

318
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:14,480
那些想举手的就不会那么害怕了
the others who wanted to would be less afraid.

319
00:17:16,090 --> 00:17:17,660
那边的就是法案吗
Is that it? The bill?

320
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,670
是  内阁会议刚开完就送来了
Yes. They delivered it just after the cabinet meeting.

321
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:25,310
也许我该签了这破法案
Maybe I should just sign the damn thing.

322
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:28,130
我拖得越久  对我的怨气就越大
The longer I wait, the bigger target I become.

323
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,580
内阁努力着呢
Well, the cabinet's working hard.

324
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:32,550
你坚持一下  给他们点时间
Stick to your guns and give them some time.

325
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:37,210
没准会拐弯  或者直接消散了
Well, it could turn. Or dissipate.

326
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:40,450
飓风温贝托和飓风费斯的轨迹一样
Hurricane Humberto was on the same trajectory as Faith.

327
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:43,190
大家都以为温贝托会夷平七个州
Everyone thought that was gonna wipe out seven states,

328
00:17:43,190 --> 00:17:45,020
结果最后拐了个弯  向南去了
but in the end, it turned south

329
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:47,330
最大风级才一级
and never became more than a Cat One.

